{"tid":2049692,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"好想講一樣野：我地既目的係光復香港，要走既唔係我地，成日見到移民post好無耐","createTime":"2020-06-03T15:19:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T16:03:19.000Z","uid":109345,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cf8acc9c2da27a8404ab917bd04c8329d12cf0a4","tid":2049692,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:19:26.000Z","msg":"唔反對大家討論， 但希望可以集中唸下點樣得到更多國際支持！ <br />\n點解美國警暴有咁強烈反應澳洲--英國都有示威，名人又支持<br />\n香港既影響力仲係好弱。明天64，我希望你地可以出來！！！！<br />\n我地既抗爭除左為自己，仲有一班：<br />\n<br />\n坐緊監既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等緊上庭既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一班00後-最有勇氣同資格但無能力移民既手足！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我求下大家 - 勿忘初心！ 光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170c57cd9d8a24576b5604a03c328ea7c4ea309e","tid":2049692,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n六四<br />\n維多利亞公園見"},{"pid":"9c4b84d5d1089a634ebcb1b8319a7e6100b99b13","tid":2049692,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:20:29.000Z","msg":"六四<br />\n維園見"},{"pid":"ffd0bc7c5b17cfcf49917ecea476084755e27a0a","tid":2049692,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0